WEBVTT

00:00.405 --> 00:03.030
I'd like to buy fifty of these hand towels, please.

00:03.461 --> 00:05.461
We're going to give them away to our customers.

00:06.665 --> 00:07.357
Thank you.

00:07.703 --> 00:09.913
The design on this towel is beautiful...

00:10.052 --> 00:11.969
...so I'm sure your customers will like them.

00:12.835 --> 00:15.007
Is it possible to give us a discount?

00:15.385 --> 00:16.400
OK.

00:17.263 --> 00:19.357
We will give you 10% discount.

00:19.995 --> 00:23.503
The price of one towel is $5.25,...

00:24.063 --> 00:28.173
...so the total amount will be $236.25.

00:29.359 --> 00:29.599
Great.

00:30.267 --> 00:32.808
And would you like us to deliver them to your office?

